  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425010/extras/3c8e993fa28eef93a747085717758220.poster.avif?t=1686585616\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425010/extras/3c8e993fa28eef93a747085717758220.webm?t=1686585616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425010/extras/3c8e993fa28eef93a747085717758220.mp4?t=1686585616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Astra is the smallest star in Constellation Station. Tired of being picked on, she sets off an adventure to build a new constellation of her own! Run, slide, jump, and glide across the galaxy while collecting stardust to build your new home in this mascot platformer develeoped entirely in the Pico-8 fantasy console. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    Fifteen levels, spanning multiple planets and diverse biomes<br></li><li>    Precise controls that allow for expressive movement<br></li><li>    Platforming challenges designed with all skill levels in mind - and a Cozy Mode with reduced hazards for a more relaxed experience<br></li><li>    Nearly 30 minutes of original music<br></li><li>    Accessibility options to ensure players can enjoy the game comfortably<br></li><li>    Speedrun support including a loadless timer and record-keeping for your individual level Personal Bests, full run PBs, and sum of bests</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425010/extras/fc4a9e251949a025684e8a62b1cd777b.poster.avif?t=1686585616\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425010/extras/fc4a9e251949a025684e8a62b1cd777b.webm?t=1686585616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425010/extras/fc4a9e251949a025684e8a62b1cd777b.mp4?t=1686585616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425010/extras/3c8e993fa28eef93a747085717758220.poster.avif?t=1686585616\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425010/extras/3c8e993fa28eef93a747085717758220.webm?t=1686585616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425010/extras/3c8e993fa28eef93a747085717758220.mp4?t=1686585616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Astra is the smallest star in Constellation Station. Tired of being picked on, she sets off an adventure to build a new constellation of her own! Run, slide, jump, and glide across the galaxy while collecting stardust to build your new home in this mascot platformer develeoped entirely in the Pico-8 fantasy console. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    Fifteen levels, spanning multiple planets and diverse biomes<br></li><li>    Precise controls that allow for expressive movement<br></li><li>    Platforming challenges designed with all skill levels in mind - and a Cozy Mode with reduced hazards for a more relaxed experience<br></li><li>    Nearly 30 minutes of original music<br></li><li>    Accessibility options to ensure players can enjoy the game comfortably<br></li><li>    Speedrun support including a loadless timer and record-keeping for your individual level Personal Bests, full run PBs, and sum of bests</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425010/extras/fc4a9e251949a025684e8a62b1cd777b.poster.avif?t=1686585616\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425010/extras/fc4a9e251949a025684e8a62b1cd777b.webm?t=1686585616\" type=\"video/